"title": "2339: Jesus Christ, example of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2339: jesus christ, example of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ sets his disciples an example, especially in servanthood, self-denial and endurance of suffering, so that they may become like him.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ calls believers to follow his example</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:14-John13:16\">JHN 13:14–13:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1\">HEB 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2-Heb12:3\">HEB 12:2–12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a></p>\n<h2>The qualities of Jesus Christ which set an example for believers</h2>\n<h3>Self-denial</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:4-Phil2:5\">PHP 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:38\">MAT 10:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:27\">LUK 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a></p>\n<h3>Endurance of suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:21–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:24-Matt10:25\">MAT 10:24–10:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:20\">JHN 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14-1Thess2:15\">1TH 2:14–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:3\">HEB 12:3</a></p>\n<h3>Service</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:25-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:25–20:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:42-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:42–10:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:13-John13:17\">JHN 13:13–13:17</a></p>\n<h3>Faithfulness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1-Heb3:2\">HEB 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Love</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Patience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:16</a></p>\n<h3>Forgiveness of others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Gentleness and humility</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a></p>\n<h3>Purity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:1\">LUK 11:1</a></p>\n<h2>God wants his people to follow Jesus Christ's example and be conformed to his image</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:49</a></p>\n<h2>Those who followed Jesus Christ's example</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a> <em>Paul</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a> <em>the converts in Thessalonica</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:60\">ACT 7:60</a> <em>Stephen is following the example set by Jesus Christ in <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">Lk 23:34</a>.</em></p>",
